                        <additions>
                            <p>
                                <locus from="LCI" to="LCI" scheme="other"/>
                                <note>Top of page, in pencil by a modern hand:<quote> LB XIX 321 806</quote>. In black ink by a modern hand: <quote>A 536</quote> (current signum). Bottom of page, in pencil by a modern hand: <quote>Inköpt 10/4 04 fr. Rosenthal, München för 80 mark</quote>. In black ink: <quote>1904/9</quote>.</note>
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                <locus from="74A" to="74A" scheme="other"/>
                                <note>In light brown ink by a 16th- or 17th century hand: Psalm 47 (<quote>Magnus dominus et Laudabilis nimis</quote>).</note>
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                <locus from="RCI" to="RCI" scheme="other"/>
