                        <provenance>
                            <p>Written at <placeName ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/place/100283">Paradiso</placeName> monastery (closed in <date when="1776"/>) in <placeName ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/place/100021">Florence</placeName> by the Birgittine brother <persName>Andrea Tiburzi</persName>, according to a note on <locus from="74v" to="74v" scheme="folios"/>.</p>
                        </provenance>
                        <provenance>
                            <p>The manuscript was at an unknown occasion purchased by <orgName ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/org/100161">Rosenthal's antiquarian bookshop</orgName> in <placeName ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/place/100057">Munich.</placeName>
                            </p>
